717
00:51:32.250 --> 00:51:34.958
Right. you're with me. sunshine!
Come here!

718
00:51:36.917 --> 00:51:38.000
Sit down!

719
00:51:40.833 --> 00:51:42.083
- Shoot him!
- I did!

720
00:51:42.083 --> 00:51:43.292
Shoot him again then!

721
00:51:49.250 --> 00:51:51.125
Stop it! Stop it! Stop it!
There's a metal plate in his head!

722
00:51:51.125 --> 00:51:52.208
