725
00:52:00.792 --> 00:52:02.000
Go on! Go on!

726
00:52:03.125 --> 00:52:05.333
Sorry. mate. Go on!

727
00:52:18.958 --> 00:52:21.000
- Ter! You all right?
- Yeah.

728
00:52:21.500 --> 00:52:23.750
I am! I blocked the window.
They can't get through.

729
00:52:23.750 --> 00:52:24.667
Great.

730
00:52:24.958 --> 00:52:26.417
Oh. bollocks!

731
00:52:26.750 --> 00:52:28.833
Get back! Put your hands up!

732
00:52:29.417 --> 00:52:30.458
Oh. leave it out. mate.

733
00:52:30.458 --> 00:52:34.375
Shut up! I'm in charge now.
And we're all going to the police.

734
00:52:34.375 --> 00:52:37.667
Don't be stupid.
We've got bigger problems now.

735
00:52:37.667 --> 00:52:40.375
I don't care!
They're all going to prison!

736
