738
00:52:44.708 --> 00:52:48.375
Oh. really? Do you...
honestly think I'm that stupid?

739
00:52:48.708 --> 00:52:51.250
Well... yeah.

740
00:52:55.167 --> 00:52:56.208
Davey!

741
00:52:57.583 --> 00:53:00.042
Please! Get it off me!
