- Clive!

745
00:53:17.833 --> 00:53:18.875
I'm fucked up. admit it.

746
00:53:18.875 --> 00:53:21.667
No. no. don't be daft. You're good as
gold. mate. Good as gold. Good as gold.

747
00:53:21.667 --> 00:53:23.958
Was it... Was it all right
the way we did the robbery?

748
00:53:24.750 --> 00:53:26.583
Yeah. no. yeah. yeah. no. textbook.

749
00:53:28.000 --> 00:53:30.208
At least... At least. it looks that way.

750
00:53:30.208 --> 00:53:33.167
Yeah. mate. As soon as we get all this
sorted. we'll be down at a pub. mate.

751
00:53:33.458 --> 00:53:35.292
We'll be alright. innit?

752
00:53:35.708 --> 00:53:36.583
Davey...

753
00:53:39.042 --> 00:53:39.917
Davey...

754
00:53:41.667 --> 00:53:42.667
I'm sorry. Andy.

755
00:53:45.417 --> 00:53:46.542
He's gone.

756
00:53:52.625 --> 00:53:54.333
We're going to the old folks' home now.

757
00:53:54.333 --> 00:53:56.208
We're gonna save granddad
and his pals. all right?

758
00:53:57.792 --> 00:53:59.208
Sweetheart.

759
00:54:01.458 --> 00:54:03.458
Go on. take it. Go on.

760
00:54:05.042 --> 00:54:08.000
Now. you can either come with us. or we
can drop you off on the way. all right?

761
00:54:09.792 --> 00:54:12.125
Well. my sister's in Marland.
Could you get me there?

762
00:54:12.417 --> 00:54:13.792
All right.

763
00:54:14.958 --> 00:54:16.500
Rest in peace. Tuppence.

764
00:54:22.042 --> 00:54:23.042
Giddy up.

765
00:54:32.208 --> 00:54:33.208
Piss off!

766
00:54:36.875 --> 00:54:39.042
We'll be okay. Ray. We'll make it.

767
00:54:39.042 --> 00:54:42.792
Yeah. no thanks to me. Look at me.
I'm bloody useless. I can't do anything.

768
00:54:43.000 --> 00:54:47.750
Oh. don't. Ray. You've got to see it.
You rescued Hamish.

769
00:54:47.750 --> 00:54:50.333
We wouldn't have been here but for you.

770
00:54:50.708 --> 00:54:54.000
I didn't rescue Hamish. I just got him
stuck in here with the rest of us.

771
00:54:54.250 --> 00:54:56.667
And now we're surrounded on all sides!

772
00:54:58.125 --> 00:54:59.875
If these fucking things get in!...

773
00:54:59.875 --> 00:55:02.042
Then we'll give 'em as good as we get!

774
00:55:24.750 --> 00:55:26.042
I've got the one with the specs.

775
00:55:26.583 --> 00:55:29.000
Hey! No! No! Easy. easy.
take this. take this. all right?

776
00:55:38.625 --> 00:55:41.667
- Get in the car!
- I'm coming. I'm coming.

777
00:55:45.417 --> 00:55:47.375
Mental's got the fucking keys! Shit!

778
00:55:47.500 --> 00:55:48.333
I'll go get 'em.

779
00:55:48.333 --> 00:55:50.542
- No. Andy. you don't need to!
- Andy. don't! It's too dangerous!

780
00:55:50.542 --> 00:55:51.708
I'll be fine!

781
00:56:00.542 --> 00:56:03.250
Hello... Uh... Okay...

782
00:56:05.125 --> 00:56:09.708
Eww... Go away... You queer thing.

783
00:56:20.125 --> 00:56:22.208
- You all right?
- Yeah...

784
00:56:55.042 --> 00:56:56.042
What are you doing here?

785
00:56:56.042 --> 00:56:59.417
Saving your arse as per fucking usual.
mate. D'you think I'm gonna let you die?

786
00:56:59.417 --> 00:57:03.250
Oh. piss off. you muppets! I'll take you
all on and so will my fucking brother!

787
00:57:03.250 --> 00:57:05.292
Fucking stop saying that. Come on.

788
00:57:06.333 --> 00:57:07.792
You better take to save your bullets.

789
00:57:08.500 --> 00:57:10.208
Yeah. but you've already
done a few. mate.

790
00:57:10.208 --> 00:57:12.125
It's not a competition. Andy!

791
00:57:13.042 --> 00:57:15.250
You can't just go running
in there on your own. bruv.

792
00:57:15.250 --> 00:57:16.792
Well. it worked out fine. didn't it?

793
00:57:16.917 --> 00:57:17.958
Yeah. this time. eh?

794
00:57:18.042 --> 00:57:20.042
- Fuck off.
- Fuck off!

795
00:57:24.417 --> 00:57:26.375
Ta-da! We've got the keys.

796
00:57:26.375 --> 00:57:28.375
I don't need keys.

797
00:57:28.458 --> 00:57:30.250
That's why you brought
me along. remember?

798
00:57:32.250 --> 00:57:35.208
Oi! Get off my car! It's a 5 series!

799
00:57:43.542 --> 00:57:46.167
What are we gonna do?
They're gonna break in.

800
00:57:46.250 --> 00:57:47.417
Well. lets get tooled up.

801
00:57:47.417 --> 00:57:50.542
open the doors and take some
of these bastards down with us!

802
00:57:50.542 --> 00:57:52.625
Are you seriously suggesting
that we let 'em all in.

803
00:57:52.625 --> 00:57:57.000
