- Yeah.

832
01:00:26.958 --> 01:00:30.667
Jen. Oh. no.

833
01:00:32.708 --> 01:00:34.500
Look. let me take care of it.

834
01:00:34.500 --> 01:00:37.583
No. no. um. they might find a cure. so...

835
01:00:53.625 --> 01:00:55.333
Well? Did you find her?

836
01:00:55.333 --> 01:00:58.250
- Uh. no. no. she wasn't. um...
