Leprechauns! What do you think?

840
01:01:29.167 --> 01:01:31.833
Can't believe this. Even when they're
zombies. they can't stand each other.

841
01:01:36.458 --> 01:01:38.542
This is just the
weirdest day of my life.

842
01:01:46.458 --> 01:01:47.750
Quick.

843
01:02:04.083 --> 01:02:06.375
Hit the road. Ter.

844
01:02:07.875 --> 01:02:09.208
It's pointless.

845
01:02:09.708 --> 01:02:10.875
