846
01:02:10.875 --> 01:02:12.667
they're bound to have gotten
to the old folks' home by now.

847
01:02:12.833 --> 01:02:13.750
You can't give up.

848
01:02:13.750 --> 01:02:15.208
If we're hunky-dory. so will granddad.

849
01:02:15.250 --> 01:02:16.208
Oh. yeah?!

850
01:02:16.208 --> 01:02:19.917
And where is that gonna happen exactly.
Andy? Lucky fucking Andy world?!

851
01:02:19.917 --> 01:02:22.625
Grow up! This place is going to shit!

852
01:02:23.000 --> 01:02:24.875
Can we just go?

853
01:02:25.458 --> 01:02:26.292
I can't do this.

854
01:02:26.292 --> 01:02:28.000
Yes. you can. Of course. you can.

855
01:02:28.458 --> 01:02:30.708
You know. I would've died about ten
times today if it wasn't for you.

856
01:02:30.708 --> 01:02:33.333
I'm only lucky 'cause you're
always there to sort me out.

857
01:02:33.375 --> 01:02:35.708
We can do this... together.

858
01:02:35.708 --> 01:02:37.833
Yeah. you... you helped me get to my
sister's house. just like you promised.

859
01:02:37.833 --> 01:02:40.417
The least I can do is help
you get to your granddad.

860
01:02:41.333 --> 01:02:43.625
I mean. we haven't even got
any bullets left. How...

861
01:02:45.125 --> 01:02:47.250
We're gonna pass Mental's
lock-up. don't we?

862
01:02:47.708 --> 01:02:48.792
Yeah. I guess so.

863
01:02:48.792 --> 01:02:50.875
His lock-up. where all his guns are.

864
01:03:08.042 --> 01:03:09.750
What in ...!

865
01:03:11.625 --> 01:03:13.125
Fuck me!

866
01:03:16.667 --> 01:03:17.833
Right.

867
01:03:20.958 --> 01:03:23.667
- Right. Ter. tool up!
- What about this?

868
01:03:23.917 --> 01:03:26.500
How about something a little
easier to handle. eh. Andy?

869
01:03:26.500 --> 01:03:28.833
- Fair enough.
- Come on then.

870
01:03:32.000 --> 01:03:33.708
- Put that in.
- Bullets.

871
01:03:39.417 --> 01:03:40.958
Sick.

872
01:03:41.625 --> 01:03:43.042
Nice.

873
01:03:44.958 --> 01:03:46.625
Go! Go! Come on!

874
01:03:50.000 --> 01:03:52.542
Guys... Are you sure we've got enough?

875
01:03:52.542 --> 01:03:53.792
Yes. come on.

876
01:03:54.792 --> 01:03:56.333
- Shit!
- What?

877
01:03:56.417 --> 01:03:59.375
The old folks. We're never gonna
fit 'em all in the car! Shit!

878
01:03:59.792 --> 01:04:01.375
We need another van.

879
01:04:06.208 --> 01:04:08.042
- Katy.
- Yeah.

880
01:04:09.500 --> 01:04:12.542
- Can you hot-wire anything?
- 'Course. Why?

881
01:04:25.583 --> 01:04:30.250
Fucking hell! Ha ha ha! Yes! Hah! Wooo!

882
01:04:39.708 --> 01:04:42.792
- Why have we stopped?
- There's a red light.

883
01:04:42.792 --> 01:04:45.000
There's no other fucking
traffic. you plum.

884
01:04:45.000 --> 01:04:45.958
Just drive!

885
01:04:46.292 --> 01:04:48.583
Just be a rebel for once in
your life. Terrence. please.

886
01:04:48.917 --> 01:04:52.292
Well. for fuck's sake!
Excuse me for obeying highway code!

887
01:04:56.042 --> 01:04:58.583
Get off our bus. you fucking mug!

888
01:05:03.042 --> 01:05:04.542
No ticket.

889
01:05:09.667 --> 01:05:11.583
- Sorry.
- It's okay.

890
01:05:11.583 --> 01:05:12.750
Yep. all right.

891
01:05:36.125 --> 01:05:37.333
Look. they might be alright.

892
01:05:37.333 --> 01:05:40.083
They probably locked themselves
in the basement or sumthink.

893
01:05:40.083 --> 01:05:41.542
I don't think there is a basement. mate.

894
01:05:41.875 --> 01:05:43.000
We need to make a diversion.

895
01:05:43.000 --> 01:05:44.042
Well. leave that to me.

896
01:05:44.042 --> 01:05:45.750
- Are you sure?
- Yeah. Okay.

897
01:05:46.333 --> 01:05:48.667
- Wait. wait. wait. wait.
- There's loads... There's loads...

898
01:05:49.125 --> 01:05:51.958
Now. take this. if we're
longer than ten minutes...

899
01:05:51.958 --> 01:05:54.000
- Then fucking wait longer.
- Will do.

900
01:05:57.125 --> 01:05:59.917
Hey. guys! Come here. you big losers!

901
01:06:00.458 --> 01:06:02.750
Woo-oo! Come on!

902
01:06:04.208 --> 01:06:05.792
Go. go. go. go!

903
01:06:09.750 --> 01:06:10.917
Let's go!

904
01:06:13.500 --> 01:06:15.542
Come on! Over here!

905
01:06:50.750 --> 01:06:53.833
There are too many of 'em.
Ain't there a safer way in?

906
01:06:55.333 --> 01:06:56.250
Skylight.

907
01:06:56.250 --> 01:06:57.833
- Yeah. go. go. go!
- Okay.

908
01:07:06.083 --> 01:07:08.792
- I'll do it.
- Right. work your magic. girl.

909
01:07:08.792 --> 01:07:10.375
- You see out?
- No.

910
01:07:16.375 --> 01:07:18.458
- Think you got twisted. luv.
