911
01:07:19.958 --> 01:07:20.958
Done.

912
01:07:23.083 --> 01:07:24.250
Careful.

913
01:07:26.792 --> 01:07:28.625
Go fuck yourselves. you zombie bastards!

914
01:07:28.625 --> 01:07:30.208
Jesus Christ!

915
01:07:32.000 --> 01:07:33.875
Terry. what are you doing here?

916
01:07:33.875 --> 01:07:37.125
We came to to save you. then you try
