919
01:07:42.667 --> 01:07:43.500
I volunteered.

920
01:07:43.500 --> 01:07:46.083
Yeah. all right. Let's get reacquainted
later. We need all of youse...

921
01:07:46.083 --> 01:07:48.667
to climb up here so we can go down
