922
01:07:48.667 --> 01:07:50.500
You're having a
"tin bath" (laugh). aintcha?

923
01:07:50.500 --> 01:07:53.333
Eric is a "Raspberry Ripple" (cripple).
Darryl's got his bad leg.

924
01:07:53.333 --> 01:07:56.542
and Hamish is on his
third hip replacement.

925
01:07:56.583 --> 01:08:00.208
Okay. is there anyone down there
that has not had a hip replacement?

926
01:08:05.500 --> 01:08:08.583
I ain't. Now come down here.
and we'll talk about it.

927
01:08:08.583 --> 01:08:09.333
All right.

928
01:08:12.042 --> 01:08:15.583
- Oh. Andy! Andy!
- All right. Doreen?

929
01:08:17.167 --> 01:08:18.833
All right. all right.
Where do we go from here?

930
01:08:18.833 --> 01:08:20.000
