- Yep.

931
01:08:20.000 --> 01:08:23.333
Oh. fuck's sake. we've
been saved. everyone.

932
01:08:23.333 --> 01:08:25.625
Laurel and fucking Hardy
here's come to rescue us.

933
01:08:25.667 --> 01:08:30.583
You haven't seen out in the lawn yet.
There's hundreds of zombies out there.

934
01:08:30.583 --> 01:08:32.250
Well. outside we've got
