935
01:08:32.250 --> 01:08:34.333
so if we can all get there.
we're laughing. all right?

936
01:08:34.333 --> 01:08:37.042
Yeah. well. we got a knife.
we got a few forks.

937
01:08:37.042 --> 01:08:39.333
and a fucking Alligator
Lopper over there.

