940
01:08:50.125 --> 01:08:51.417
Right. who wants this?

941
01:08:52.333 --> 01:08:53.542
Uzi 9 millimetre.

942
01:08:54.958 --> 01:08:58.500
Remember. finger off the trigger.
till you're ready to shoot.

943
01:08:58.958 --> 01:09:00.917
- Thank you. thank you very much.
