945
01:09:14.333 --> 01:09:15.208
Wow!

946
01:09:15.208 --> 01:09:17.250
All right. so you know
what to do with this. yeah?

947
01:09:17.250 --> 01:09:18.167
Of course I do.

948
01:09:19.792 --> 01:09:23.292
- Sorry.
