- Granddad!
- Go. granddad!

1037
01:18:16.667 --> 01:18:18.167
- Granddad!
- Granddad!

1038
01:18:20.750 --> 01:18:23.125
Go away! Fuck off!

1039
01:18:30.667 --> 01:18:33.458
- Fuck off! Fuck off!
- Don't fucking shoot him!

1040
